442
00:20:19,612 --> 00:20:21,403
"I want to be with older brother."

443
00:20:21,404 --> 00:20:22,886
"I want to date older brother."

444
00:20:22,887 --> 00:20:24,903
"I want to sleep with older brother."

445
00:20:24,904 --> 00:20:27,288
How is that possible?

446
00:20:27,289 --> 00:20:29,908
By the way, are you really certain

447
00:20:29,909 --> 00:20:33,308
that you can win over a girl
to this degree in only a week?

448
00:20:33,309 --> 00:20:35,107
You must confront the reality.

449
00:20:35,108 --> 00:20:37,804
Do not bring me back
to reality all of a sudden.

450
00:20:37,805 --> 00:20:40,305
I don't want to hear
this kind of grandstanding.

451
00:20:42,596 --> 00:20:46,987
Just let me dream a little longer.

452
00:20:47,599 --> 00:20:50,409
I was not expecting
the thief to steal the ring.

453
00:20:51,002 --> 00:20:53,257
We really can't make up for this sin.

454
00:20:54,001 --> 00:20:56,502
You both have already
put in a lot of effort.

455
00:20:57,202 --> 00:20:59,008
Do not be so hard on yourself.

456
00:20:59,893 --> 00:21:01,498
Appreciate your understanding.

457
00:21:07,898 --> 00:21:10,399
That ring comes with a condition.

458
00:21:11,206 --> 00:21:13,111
As a reward

459
00:21:13,112 --> 00:21:14,034
for beating the Devil King,

460
00:21:14,704 --> 00:21:18,607
the hero can marry the princess.

461
00:21:20,295 --> 00:21:21,404
Brother…

462
00:21:23,608 --> 00:21:26,904
I hope he will cherish the ring.

463
00:23:00,700 --> 00:23:01,997
The sacred treasure…

464
00:23:01,998 --> 00:23:05,486
You mean that the thief
not only took my sacred treasure

465
00:23:05,487 --> 00:23:07,711
but also sealed it?

466
00:23:08,193 --> 00:23:09,909
Get it back!

467
00:23:10,387 --> 00:23:12,403
That's impossible.

468
00:23:12,404 --> 00:23:15,017
I did not expect the sacred treasure
to be sealed.

469
00:23:15,018 --> 00:23:17,107
I have already used up all my options.

470
00:23:17,604 --> 00:23:20,392
You useless fellow!

471
00:23:20,393 --> 00:23:22,299
When exactly will you make

472
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:25,111
my wish come true?

473
00:23:31,044 --> 00:23:31,993
(Episode 7: Rest in Peace,
The Upstart Adventurer)

474
00:23:31,994 --> 00:23:33,702
I am Sylvia.

475
00:23:33,703 --> 00:23:36,397
I have completely gotten used
to vacationing.

476
00:23:36,398 --> 00:23:38,195
This feeling of freedom

477
00:23:38,911 --> 00:23:39,904
